data.description: WOW! New Roof Installation 2024. This four ( 4 ) bedroom, (2) bathroom, (2) car garage home boast an open concept floor plan with many upgrades. Large Vinyl privacy fenced back yard with covered front porch. This home features Stainless Steel Appliances, breakfast bar and kitchen with  Built in Shelves, and Large Pantry,   Gorgeous light fixtures and laminate and ceramic tile throughout. Over 2000 under air. The Master Bedroom features a Roman Tub and a lot of Privacy in this Split Floor Plan separated by  Large Living Room and Spacious Family Room. There are Loads of Closets in these spacious large bedrooms. Easy access to turnpike and i95. 20 minutes to all beaches and 5 minutes to shopping. All you need is your toothbrush to move in and make it your home-sweet-home.
